\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Brookside dairy is also still a large player, but the latest figures we
 could find still put it way behind Pearl in terms of processing capacity
 (560,000 liters per day).
 Located in Kampala, the processor sources milk from different areas.
 According to the data we collected from milk collection centers in the
 central milk shed, about 40 percent of the milk collection centers supply
 processors take their milk to Brookside.
 Jesa is another large processor with processing facilities in Busujju in
